{"tid":1514443,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】央視宣佈香港正式回歸英國！","createTime":"2019-08-28T17:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:17:31.000Z","uid":193565,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"949701e14868d6c523e79970bd9a72be8aad8c60","tid":1514443,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:41:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9SAVeCcfj4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DI9SAVeCcfj4&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=ee53bdc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9SAVeCcfj4</a><br />\n<br />\n8月20號央視指出《中英聯合聲明》係「過時無效」，我地黎睇一睇《中英聯合聲明》嘅內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cmab.gov.hk/tc/issues/jd2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmab.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fissues%2Fjd2.htm&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=0b69b31a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cmab.gov.hk/tc/issues/jd2.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n當中關鍵嘅兩點就係：<br />\n一、中華人民共和國政府聲明：收回香港地區（包括香港島、九龍和&ldquo;新界&rdquo;，以下稱香港）是全中國人民的共同願望，中華人民共和國政府決定於一九九七年七月一日對香港恢復行使主權。<br />\n<br />\n二、聯合王國政府聲明：聯合王國政府於一九九七年七月一日將香港交還給中華人民共和國。<br />\n<br />\n如果呢份聲明係「過時無效」，即係央視否認中國喺1997年7月1日收回香港主權。換言之，<span style=\"color: red;\">等同宣佈香港而家仍然係英國（上述聯合王國）殖民地</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">英國快d黎接番我哋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34fe34055c88cdd8a1157eda86f771fc27b4daf","tid":1514443,"uid":185121,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />英國自己搞唔點既話可以比返中華民國都ok。"},{"pid":"3b1ba8432cf8f3d8f16d870abd28381de7133235","tid":1514443,"uid":193565,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f34fe34055c88cdd8a1157eda86f771fc27b4daf","tid":1514443,"uid":185121,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />英國自己搞唔點既話可以比返中華民國都ok。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:45:31.000Z","msg":"總之我地而家仲係英屬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f813cac639c7048bf4c7314fd25f8e1aa18da3","tid":1514443,"uid":197393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f34fe34055c88cdd8a1157eda86f771fc27b4daf","tid":1514443,"uid":185121,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />英國自己搞唔點既話可以比返中華民國都ok。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:46:29.000Z","msg":"唔好搞唔掂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314073b5f3e228b4ddaa9182ccc616404d92d6c1","tid":1514443,"uid":158718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:47:11.000Z","msg":"嘩！ 笑話一則！"},{"pid":"384a5044098e67cc6e2dc00a70730538117c46fb","tid":1514443,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:48:57.000Z","msg":"英國人最睇唔起華人，咪on 9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f93ef33b3a9b45d47fd22f33ce2b4e8ed6264df","tid":1514443,"uid":193565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"384a5044098e67cc6e2dc00a70730538117c46fb","tid":1514443,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:48:57.000Z","msg":"英國人最睇唔起華人，咪on 9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"