0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:15:25.000Z","msg":"按正常情況係可以宣佈條約無效並返回條約生效前既status, 不過係有EXCEPTION既<br />\n就係如果條約涉及領土轉讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係冇得因為一方違約而收回<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4dc84e33c8fee484690457a193320430cb1839","tid":1514443,"uid":96169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"384a5044098e67cc6e2dc00a70730538117c46fb","tid":1514443,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:48:57.000Z","msg":"英國人最睇唔起華人，咪on 9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:15:31.000Z","msg":"我識既英國人都對香港人好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bf46a9758f02f850d0537433930160e0f9b980","tid":1514443,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:25:02.000Z","msg":"還我英女皇生日假"},{"pid":"4dd320072e2b2953c1d4ccfb8221094342ec37f2","tid":1514443,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"光復香港, 不要支籍<br />\n&ldquo;中國單方面宣稱中英聯合聲明已經失效，香港人該何去何從？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n用1分鐘嘅時間簽名，務求收集到10萬簽名將BNO平權議題推上議會討論<br />\n註: 轉BC後可傳俾97後<br />\n為咗你自己，仲有你嘅摯愛，簽名？刻不容緩<br />\n<br />\nPostal Code 請填000000，如果身處英國就填所在地點嘅Code<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=f551ec2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"}]}